code: export function groupAttributesBySet(attributes){return attributes.reduce((acc,attribute)=>{const setName=attribute.attribute_set.name;if(!acc[setName]){acc[setName]=[];}acc[setName].push(attribute);return acc;},{});}export const normalizeAttributes=attributes=>{const sortedKeys=Object.keys(attributes).sort();const normalizedAttributes={};sortedKeys.forEach(key=>{normalizedAttributes[key]=attributes[key];});return normalizedAttributes;};
